{"TopicId":172705,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Music and Ambient Sounds","CreatedByName":"viperwolf","CreatedById":66190,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-20T03:39:03Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"viperwolf","CreatedById":66190,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-20T03:39:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you turn off the music without it turning off the background noise?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-20T22:43:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGo to settings and turn the music slider to zero.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI highly recommend keeping it though, it really grows on you.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"viperwolf","CreatedById":66190,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T00:03:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223329344\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172705\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521585834\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGo to settings and turn the music slider to zero.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI highly recommend keeping it though, it really grows on you.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThats the problem, when you turn it to zero you lose the other ambient sounds, like the crickets outside the buildings. Ive listened to that music for years lol, Im kinda tired of it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-03-21T00:04:16Z\u0022 title=\u002203/21/2018 12:04  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 21, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by viperwolf\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T02:39:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSounds like a bug to me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReport it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T08:23:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBetcha it\u0027s not a bug. I\u0027d bet the cricket noises and such at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E are treated as a music file.\u00A0 I\u0027ve never had music in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E view, just ambients.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T13:03:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223329750\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172705\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521620585\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBetcha it\u0027s not a bug. I\u0027d bet the cricket noises and such at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E are treated as a music file.\u00A0 I\u0027ve never had music in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E view, just ambients.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrue, more like a bad design decision I suppose.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}